# Cloudflare Pages redirects for www.oftmw.com.
#
# The Studio admin used to live at /studio/* on this site; it's now its own
# Cloudflare Access-gated deployment at admin.oftmw.com. Catch every bookmark
# and transparently bounce to the canonical admin. The trailing 301! forces
# the redirect even if a file by the same path exists in the bundle.
/studio/* https://admin.oftmw.com/:splat 301!
